<br>
One of the absolute worst places to fight is at the entrance to the level.  We had invis break there once and I swear we fought non-stop for literally 30 minutes or so.  We ended up having to go through the locked door right there and killing the roamer there so that we could med up enough to handle any occurrences that might come up on our run through again.<br>
<br>
All in all, ToFS is a great zone...unless you die in it.  They really need to make those keys soublound and maybe have it set up so that the keys on higher levels will unlock all of the lower level mirrors.  I hate having a backpack in the bank full of keys for that one dungeon.  We made a ton of experience there with our group and had fun doing it.  Level 6 is pretty good experience clear up to 51 or so, and plat/weapon drops are plentiful.  Now that I think about it, we never did kill Tserrina...I think maybe we will need to head back there.&lt;G&gt;<br>
<br>
