<br>
I have spent a ton of time in the Tower and know it very well.<br>
<br>
Floor 4 can be very dangerous moving thru and is alot tougher than Floor 5 or 6 imo.<br>
<br>
The best stragegy for moving thru it I have found is too move your group to the hall just before the shadows.  Right after you pass thru the hidden wall there is a rather long empty hallway. This is the spot I am talking about.<br>
<br>
There are no static spawns in this hall.  There are three roamers that come thru and one of them is the mummy that occasionaly can see thru inviso.  Set up in the hall and take the three roamers here.<br>
<br>
After you kill them inviso up and its now safe to move past the Shadows and to the mirror.  Cara Ominca does not see inviso at least any time I have passed her.<br>
<br>
Just another tid bit here.<br>
<br>
Floor 7 is the best exp I have found up to Level 55.  Much stronger than Velks spiders and Casters can solo there starting at about Level 50.<br>
